Compile:
Type "make" in the terminal.

Change Nick of the bot:
The nick is passed into the bot in main.cpp
If you need to change the nick of the bot, change that part in main.cpp.

Channel to join:
Channel information is stored in the file "config".
The bot will read this file to get the channel information.
This file must exist.

Execute:
Execute the program "bot".
The bot will automatically connect to the irc and channel provided.

Functions provided:
@repeat, @play, @guess, @cal, @help.
You can type @help in the irc channel to ask the bot for further information.
